@{
    ViewBag.Title = "Contact";
}
<div class="container-fluid p-0 m-0 overlayDiv">
    <div class="card">
        <div class="card-body">
            <h5 class="card-title">ADVICE AND RESPONSES</h5>
            <div class="row  no-gutters AvatarQ4">
                <div class="card-header text-center" style="background-color: #f0f2f6">
                    <video class="mycedio" id="Q4Advice1" width="70%" height="auto">
                        <source src="~/Media/eng/Q4-Advice.mp4" type='video/mp4;'>
                    </video>
                    <br />
                    <i class="fa fa-play-circle-o myHTMLvideo" id="Q4Advice" style="color: red;font-size: 2.5em;"></i>
                    @*<Button class="animate-button btn-sm btn-close-white myHTMLvideo" id="Q4">Click here to listen instructions</Button>*@
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-12 col-sm-12 col-md-6 col-lg-12">
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <div class="col-12">
                            <p class="text-black lead">
                                It looks like you will need specialist help for your overall mental health and so, for this reason,
                                I will message the team and move you to a higher priority in the team’s waiting list. <strong>
    Please note, if you feel like you need help today then please call …</strong> (probably 111, but maybe a different helpline in each Trust) or 999
                                if you need urgent help right now – for example, if you have thoughts to harm yourself or others currently. Otherwise,
                                I can confirm that you will need to see a specialist and that they should be in touch before too long. To repeat, however,
                                do contact the emergency numbers if you need urgent help.
                                <div class="alert alert-danger align-items-center" role="alert">
                                    <svg width="20px" height="20px" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="bi bi-exclamation-triangle-fill flex-shrink-0 me-2" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Warning:">
                                        <path d="M8.982 1.566a1.13 1.13 0 0 0-1.96 0L.165 13.233c-.457.778.091 1.767.98 1.767h13.713c.889 0 1.438-.99.98-1.767L8.982 1.566zM8 5c.535 0 .954.462.9.995l-.35 3.507a.552.552 0 0 1-1.1 0L7.1 5.995A.905.905 0 0 1 8 5zm.002 6a1 1 0 1 1 0 2 1 1 0 0 1 0-2z" />
                                    </svg>
                                    Emergency <strong>999</strong>
                                    <br />
                                    <svg width="20px" height="20px" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="bi bi-exclamation-triangle-fill flex-shrink-0 me-2" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Warning:">
                                        <path d="M8.982 1.566a1.13 1.13 0 0 0-1.96 0L.165 13.233c-.457.778.091 1.767.98 1.767h13.713c.889 0 1.438-.99.98-1.767L8.982 1.566zM8 5c.535 0 .954.462.9.995l-.35 3.507a.552.552 0 0 1-1.1 0L7.1 5.995A.905.905 0 0 1 8 5zm.002 6a1 1 0 1 1 0 2 1 1 0 0 1 0-2z" />
                                    </svg>
                                    National non-emergency medical number<strong> 111</strong>
                                </div>
                            </p>
                            <p class="text-black lead">
                                Thank you for connecting with our assessment system. All the best, and I look forward to you receiving the help you need soon.
                            </p>
                            <br /><br />
                            <div class="row  text-center SectionEndSession">
                                <div class="col-12 col-sm-12 col-md-12 col-lg-12">
                                    @*<button id="EndSession" type="button" class="btn btn-info btn-lg" name="submit">End Session</button>*@
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
@section scripts {
    <script src="~/Scripts/site.js"></script>
}